ce: Rousey vs. Kaufman\">Strikeforce: Rousey vs. Kaufman</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>Strikeforce: Rockhold vs. Kennedy</b></i> was a <a href=\"/wiki/Mixed_martial_arts\" title=\"Mixed martial arts\">mixed martial arts</a> event held by <a href=\"/wiki/Strikeforce_(mixed_martial_arts)\" title=\"Strikeforce (mixed martial arts)\">Strikeforce</a>. The event took place on July 14, 2012 at the <a href=\"/wiki/Rose_Garden_(arena)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Rose Garden (arena)\">Rose Garden</a> in <a href=\"/wiki/Portland,_Oregon\" title=\"Portland, Oregon\">Portland</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Oregon\" title=\"Oregon\">Oregon</a>.<sup id=\"cite&#95;ref-Strikeforce&#95;41&#95;1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Strikeforce_41-1\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>1<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>\n</p>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Results\">Results</h2><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Strikeforce:_Rockhold_vs._Kennedy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Results\"><span>edit</span></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></div>\n<table class=\"toccolours\" style=\"font-size: 85%;\">\n\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"8\" style=\"background-color: #ccf; color: #000080; text-align: center;\">Main card (Showtime)\n</th></tr>\n\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Weight class\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Method\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Round\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Time\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Middleweight\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Luke_Rockhold\" title=\"Luke Rockhold\">Luke Rockhold</a> (c)\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;padding-right:5px\">def.\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\"><a href=\"/wiki/Tim_Kennedy_(fighter)\" title=\"Tim Kennedy (fighter)\">Tim Kennedy</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Decision (unanimous) (49–46, 49–46, 49–46)\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">5\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">5:00\n</td>\n<td><sup id=\"cite&#95;ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>a<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Welterweight\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Nate_Marquardt\" title=\"Nate Marquardt\">Nate Marquardt</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;padding-right:5px\">def.\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\"><a href=\"/wiki/Tyron_Woodley\" title=\"Tyron Woodley\">Tyron Woodley</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">KO (elbows and punches)\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">4\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">1:39\n</td>\n<td><sup id=\"cite&#95;ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>b<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Middleweight\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Roger_Gracie\" title=\"Roger Gracie\">Roger Gracie</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;padding-right:5px\">def.\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\"><a href=\"/wiki/Keith_Jardine\" title=\"Keith Jardine\">Keith Jardine</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Decision (unanimous) (29–27, 30–27, 30–26)\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">3\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">5:00\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Middleweight\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Lorenz_Larkin\" title=\"Lorenz Larkin\">Lorenz Larkin</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;padding-right:5px\">def.\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\"><a href=\"/wiki/Robbie_Lawler\" title=\"Robbie Lawler\">Robbie Lawler</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Decision (unanimous) (30–27, 30–27, 30–27)\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">3\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">5:00\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"8\" style=\"background-color: #ccf; color: #000080; text-align: center;\">Preliminary card (Showtime Extreme)\n</th></tr>\n\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Weight class\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Method\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Round\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Time\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Lightweight\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Pat_Healy_(fighter)\" title=\"Pat Healy (fighter)\">Pat Healy</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;padding-right:5px\">def.\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\"><a href=\"/wiki/Mizuto_Hirota\" title=\"Mizuto Hirota\">Mizuto Hirota</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Decision (unanimous) (30–27, 29–28, 29–28)\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">3\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">5:00\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Lightweight\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Ryan_Couture\" title=\"Ryan Couture\">Ryan Couture</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;padding-right:5px\">def.\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\"><a href=\"/wiki/Joe_Duarte\" title=\"Joe Duarte\">Joe Duarte</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Decision (split) (29–28, 28–29, 29–28)\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">3\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">5:00\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Lightweight\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Jorge_Masvidal\" title=\"Jorge Masvidal\">Jorge Masvidal</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;padding-right:5px\">def.\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\"><a href=\"/wiki/Justin_Wilcox_(martial_arts)\" title=\"Justin Wilcox (martial arts)\">Justin Wilcox</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Decision (split) (29–28, 28–29, 30–27)\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">3\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">5:00\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Welterweight\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Jordan_Mein\" title=\"Jordan Mein\">Jordan Mein</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;padding-right:5px\">def.\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\"><a href=\"/wiki/Tyler_Stinson\" title=\"Tyler Stinson\">Tyler Stinson</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Decision (unanimous) (30–27, 30–27, 30–27)\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">3\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">5:00\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Welterweight\n</td>\n<td 